                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ci-cassandra.apache.org/job/Cassandra-devbranch/479/testReport/junit/org.apache.cassandra.db.marshal/ValueAccessorTest/testSlice/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://ci-cassandra.apache.org/job/Cassandra-devbranch/479/testReport/junit/org.apache.cassandra.db.marshal/ValueAccessorTest/testSlice/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

